data.description: Alert! HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!This exquisite home is designed for seamless entertaining, boasting abundant space flooded with natural light, lofty ceilings, and inviting airy environments. The living area is ideal for hosting gatherings, and creating cherished memories in a welcoming ambiance. The kitchen is a culinary haven, ample counter and cabinet space, and a modern color palette that exudes tranquility. Picture yourself on the lanai, savoring your favorite beverage, reveling in breathtaking sunsets, and taking in the splendid water views. Upstairs, the expansive owner's suite beckons with a generously sized walk-in closet and an indulgent ensuite.. The  additional well-appointed bedrooms with ample storage complete the upper level. Live the Florida's lifestyle,at Concord Station, with its resort-style amenities including community pool, playground, basketball court, tennis courts, and clubhouse!  These amenities ensure an enjoyable family experience. Proximity to top-rated schools, excellent healthcare facilities, premier shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as convenient access to major highways, enhances the appeal of this residence. Seize the opportunity to become the proud owner of this lovingly maintained home.A/C 2020  Roof 2009
